quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,60,"Wallatheena yu/toona maataw waquloobuhum wajilatun annahum ila rabbihim rajiAAoon"
  23,61,"Ola-ika yusariAAoona feealkhayrati wahum laha sabiqoon"
  23,62,"Wala nukallifu nafsan illawusAAaha waladayna kitabun yantiqu bilhaqqiwahum la yuthlamoon"
  23,63,"Bal quloobuhum fee ghamratin min hathawalahum aAAmalun min dooni thalika hum lahaAAamiloon"
  23,64,"Hatta itha akhathnamutrafeehim bilAAathabi itha hum yaj-aroon"
  23,65,"La taj-aroo alyawma innakum minnala tunsaroon"
  23,66,"Qad kanat ayatee tutlaAAalaykum fakuntum AAala aAAqabikum tankisoon"
  23,67,"Mustakbireena bihi samiran tahjuroon"
  23,68,"Afalam yaddabbaroo alqawla am jaahumma lam ya/ti abaahumu al-awwaleen"
  23,69,"Am lam yaAArifoo rasoolahum fahum lahumunkiroon"
  23,70,"Am yaqooloona bihi jinnatun bal jaahumbilhaqqi waaktharuhum lilhaqqi karihoon"
  23,71,"Walawi ittabaAAa alhaqqu ahwaahumlafasadati assamawatu wal-arduwaman feehinna bal ataynahum bithikrihim fahum AAanthikrihim muAAridoon"
  23,72,"Am tas-aluhum kharjan fakharajurabbika khayrun wahuwa khayru arraziqeen"
  23,73,"Wa-innaka latadAAoohum ila siratinmustaqeem"
  23,74,"Wa-inna allatheena layu/minoona bil-akhirati AAani assiratilanakiboon"
